<H3> <TI>   MONTSAME Carries Press Reviews </TI></H3>
<H4>   Press Review for 17 Mar </H4>
<F P=102> OW1703162994 Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME in English 1544 GMT 17 Mar 
94 -- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

