<H3> <TI>   State Great Hural Member Meets Russia's Gaydar </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  OW1503193494 Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME in English 1824 GMT 15 Mar 
94 -- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> OW1503193494 </F>
<F P=104>  Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Ulaanbaatar, March 15 (OANA-MONTSAME) -- The 
well-known figure of the opposition forces of Mongolia, State 
Great Hural member D. Ganbold on his way from Germany to 
homeland stopped in Moscow, where he had a meeting with the 
leader of the party "Vybor Rossii" ("Choice of Russia") Yegor 
Gaydar. 
  The chairman of the Mongolian National Democratic Party D. 
Ganbold also earlier, holding the post of the first vice prime 
minister of the country, made attempts to establish contact with 
Yegor Gaydar. Two years ago his meeting with Gaydar had failed 
as a plane with him on board has arrived in Moscow late. 

</TEXT>

