<H3> <TI>   New Leaders Expected for Social Democratic Party </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  OW1803194894 Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME in English 1714 GMT 18 Mar 
94--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> OW1803194894 </F>
<F P=104>  Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Ulaanbaatar, March 18 (OANA-MONTSAME) -- As is 
known from reliable sources, it is expected that the leadership 
of the Mongolian Social Democratic Party would be changed and 
renewed substantially. The leaders of the party seemed to 
decide to give up their places to new persons. The issue on 
this point would be settled by more than hundred of delegates of 
the forthcoming congress of the Social Democratic Party to be 
held from 10 to 10 March [dates as received]. 

</TEXT>

