<F P=100> ANNEX </F>
<F P=101> Mongolia </F>
<H3> <TI>   Commission Says Repression Victims Rehabilitated </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  OW1803200094 Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME in English 1720 GMT 18 Mar 
94--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> OW1803200094 </F>
<F P=104>  Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Ulaanbaatar, March 18 (OANA-MONTSAME) -- For the 
last years some 27 thousand people having been subjected to 
repression for political reasons have been rehabilitated. At 
present there are cases of about eight thousand people having 
been victims of the 30s- 40s repressions are still awaiting to 
be checked and settled. This was said by the State 
Rehabilitation Commission. 

</TEXT>

