Movement of the Congo; Leon Nzokene, general secretary of the 
Congolese Socialist Party; Kamba Raymond, general secretary of 
the Congolese Communist Party; Amoussouvi Vignik Amedegnato, 
general secretary of the Togolese People's Rally; Mohamed Bel 
Hadj Amor, general secretary of the People's Unity Party of 
