<H3> <TI>   Russian Envoy Hosts Banquet on Treaty Anniversary </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  SK1903054994 Pyongyang Korean Central Broadcasting Network 
in Korean 1300 GMT 17 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> SK1903054994 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang Korean Central Broadcasting Network 
in Korean 1300 GMT 17 Mar 94 </F>



<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105>Korean </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Yuriy Fadeyev, ambassador of the Russian 
Federation, arranged a banquet on the evening of 17 March at the 
Embassy to commemorate the 45th anniversary of the signing of 
the economic and cultural cooperation treaty between the DPRK 
and Russia. 
  Functionaries concerned, including Yi Song-tae, chairman of 
the External Economic Committee; (Yun Kyong-nam), vice minister 
of Culture and Art; (Kim Yong-su), vice chairman of the 
Committee for Cultural Relations with Foreign Countries; and Yi 
Pong-hui, chairman of the DPRK-Russia Friendship Association and 
vice chairman of the DPRK Radio and Television Broadcasting 
Committee were invited to the banquet. 
  Speeches were delivered at the Banquet. 

</TEXT>

