<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, March 19 (KCNA) -- The Central Committee 
of the Workers' Party of Korea [WPK] sent messages to foreign 
parties in reply to their messages of greetings on the birthday 
of the dear leader Comrade Kim Chong-il . 
  The reply messages were addressed to the Central Committee 
of 
the Communist Party of India (Marxist), the Central Committee of 
the Mozambique Liberation Front Party, the Central Executive 
