Chi Minh City and said that Vietnam and Thailand have favourable 
conditions for the further development of their relations. 
  At the end of the Thai prime minister's visit, the two sides 
released a joint press communique which says among other things 
that the Vietnamese Government expressed sincere thanks to the 
Thai Government for granting economic and technical aid worth 40 
million baht to Vietnam in 1994. 

